{"tid":428433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葵盛東邨男子墮樓 揭發屋內老婦幾被斬甩頭","createTime":"2017-10-08T05:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T09:46:49.000Z","uid":122,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"a41c4f981e55a205d04b42251a9b04070f6f5ccc","tid":428433,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:12:39.000Z","msg":"<strong>葵盛東邨男子墮樓 揭發屋內老婦幾被斬甩頭</strong><br />\n<br />\n即時突發  2017-10-08 12:59:40 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n中午12時，葵盛東邨盛安樓對開，一名年約30多歲男子由16樓墮下，撞到一棵樹後倒在山坡上，送院救治，警方接報到場調查期間，揭發一名老婦在男子墮樓單位內倒卧床上，頭部幾被斬甩，當場慘死。警方正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41df72acf6d37d4eb6886c0c5d7b1b318da06062","tid":428433,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:13:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d373fcc408302614b50c8bd0f0b9d8e2c72a5bf5","tid":428433,"uid":53122,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:14:04.000Z","msg":"連登廢青啃老族"},{"pid":"bac01d9f622e99ffe4c7f7fb0069ba9327b9e859","tid":428433,"uid":116157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:14:08.000Z","msg":"wtf"},{"pid":"b23edf3b496c6e0c1156424e6e336e370637b158","tid":428433,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e316f674f4a14914941a132207e2833c7efa0679","tid":428433,"uid":24282,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:14:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/131420_39ca223a2e07d521d225bb1b12cd7901.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F131420_39ca223a2e07d521d225bb1b12cd7901.png&h=2bae8e87&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54b303cdc7320a7d5e3ec84894975157f4bce08b","tid":428433,"uid":73613,"like":35,"disl